textBeforeTable: Individual stats Olympus tops Provo, advances Related See all 39 game photos » Photos Trailing by one at the half, Olympus raced to a double-digit lead early in the third quarter and never looked back in a convincing victory over Provo in the 4A semifinals at the Maverik Center. The Titans outscored the Bulldogs 40-26 in the second half. Will Cannon led the way for Olympus with 24 points, with Nick Barney adding 15, 10 of which came in the first half.Adam Finch led Provo with 14 points, with Jonny Flake chipping in with 10 points and 13 rebounds.
